6. THE OMAHON SEAL

   Every legitimate copy of Alfred Linux carries the Omahon Seal.
   The seal verifies:
   - Build integrity (HMAC-SHA256 chain of trust)
   - Runtime tamper detection (inotify watchman)
   - Sovereign attestation (builder identity)
   - Chain of provenance back to The Commander

   A system with a broken or missing Omahon Seal is NOT an
   authorized copy of Alfred Linux and carries NO blessing,
   warranty, or covenant protection.

